thread.title: The Key to Winning in Women’s Tennis: Create More Offense

author: Tom Perrotta
title: The Key to Winning in Women’s Tennis: Create More Offense
text:
Paris
After winning her first-round match at the French Open on Sunday, Elina Svitolina briefly talked to reporters, stretched out and warmed up again, and went out to Court 16 to practice. Her main objective: Crush every forehand and backhand her coach sent her way.
